1. String Immutable
==> Cannot change the value of original string memory in HEAP

String Object             >> heap
String Literal >>> winner >> constant pool

2. String Mutable
StringBuilder => single thread    >> heap
StringBuffer  => multiple threads >> heap

Speed: StringBuilder >> StringBuffer >> String Literal

v String s = "a,b,c,d"
x StringBuilder s = new StringBuilder("a,b,c,d");